Class Property

java.lang.Object
main.Property
public class Property
extends java.lang.Object
The Property class stores details about a property based on an information from the csv files.

      Constructor specifying property information
      Parameters:
      eircode - the String with full Eircode/postcode
      address - the String with full address without commas
      estMarketValue - the int for estimated market value of property
      locationCategory - the String with location type of the property
      principalPrivateRes - the String "YES" or "NO" depending whether this priperty is principal residence of current owner
      curOwnerId - the String for unique ID, PPSN of current property owner
